structures, and target business domains.\",\n    artifacts: [\"Sovereign DAG Topology Design\", \"90-Day Execution Roadmap\"],\n    toolLabel: \"Generate Blueprint\",\n    toolHref: \"/build/blueprint\",\n    metric: \"Interactive Architecture\"\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"workshop\",\n    num: 4,\n    label: \"Workshop\",\n    duration: \"1-2 Days\",\n    description: \"Collaborative threat-modeling and system configuration session with core GFF AI systems engineers to validate network edge connectors.\",\n    artifacts: [\"Integration Schema Validation\", \"Secured Subnet Design Spec\"],\n    toolLabel: \"Inquire Now\",\n    toolHref: \"/build/talk\",\n    metric: \"Joint Technical Validation\"\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"proposal\",\n    num: 5,\n    label: \"Proposal\",\n    duration: \"48 Hours\",\n    description: \"Receive a formal, algorithmic Statement of Work (SOW), delivery timeline, operational service levels (SLAs), and PPT presentation deck.\",\n    artifacts: [\"Custom Statement of Work (SOW)\", \"Enterprise Commercial Plan\"],\n    toolLabel: \"Open Proposal Studio\",\n    toolHref: \"/build/proposal\",\n    metric: \"Automated Core Pricing\"\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"contract\",\n    num: 6,\n    label: \"Contract\",\n    duration: \"1-2 Weeks\",\n    description: \"Review and execute SOC2-compliant agreements. Lock down dedicated single-tenant cloud boundaries or arrange local air-gapped license terms.\",\n    artifacts: [\"Sovereign Private License SLA\", \"Data Confidentiality Pact\"],\n    toolLabel: \"Review Sandbox Specs\",\n    toolHref: \"/build/sandbox\",\n    metric: \"Full Regulatory Compliance\"\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"delivery\",\n    num: 7,\n    label: \"Delivery\",\n    duration: \"30 Days\",\n    description: \"Assemble multi-agent workflows inside GFF Foundry Studio. Connect production APIs, cache vector databases, and implement real-time safety guardrails.\",\n    artifacts: [\"Active Cognitive Agent Fleet\", \"Sovereign Integration Mesh\"],\n    toolLabel: \"Simulate Foundry\",\n    toolHref: \"/build/foundry-studio\",\n    metric: \"Guaranteed Rapid Deploy\"\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"operate\",\n    num: 8,\n    label: \"Operate\",\n    duration: \"Continuous\",\n    description: \"Run live, autonomous, high-throughput pipelines. Our supervisor nodes continually audit schemas and balance workloads with zero data retention.\",\n    artifacts: [\"Real-time Supervisor Logs\", \"Model Compliance Telemetry\"],\n    toolLabel: \"Interact with Agent\",\n    toolHref: \"/build/talk\",\n    metric: \"99.9% Task Success rate\"\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"expand\",\n    num: 9,\n    label: \"Expand\",\n    duration: \"Ongoing\",\n    description: \"Unlock specialized agent cohorts, license validated marketplace connectors, and scale computational nodes dynamically as ROI expands.\",\n    artifacts: [\"Cohort Expansion Blueprint\", \"ROI Optimization Models\"],\n    toolLabel: \"Browse Marketplace\",\n    toolHref: \"/build/marketplace\",\n    metric: \"Multiplied Efficiency Gains\"\n  }\n];\n\nexport default function BuildHubPage() {\n  const [activeStage, setActiveStage] = useState<JourneyStage>(JOURNEY_STAGES[0]);\n\n  const tools = [\n    {\n      title: \"Readiness Assessor\",\n      href: \"/build/assessment\",\n      desc: \"Measure core infrastructure readiness across data pipelines, isolation subnets, and compliance telemetry with detailed reporting.\",\n      category: \"ASSESSMENT\",\n      color: \"from-blue-500/20 to-cyan-500/10\",\n      accent: \"#009DFF\"\n    },\n    {\n      title: \"Blueprint Architect\",\n      href: \"/build/blueprint\",\n      desc: \"Generate highly tailored multi-agent execution roadmaps based on security perimeters, workflows, and target ROI indexes.\",\n      category: \"ROADMAP\",\n      color: \"from-purple-500/20 to-pink-500/10\",\n      accent: \"#9D00FF\"\n    },\n    {\n      title: \"Operational ROI Calculator\",\n      href: \"/build/roi\",\n      desc: \"Quantify financial and administrative gains. Map labor cost multipliers, processes automated, and dynamic hardware saving estimates.\",\n      category: \"FINANCIALS\",\n      color: \"from-[#E4000F]/20 to-amber-500/10\",\n      accent: \"#E4000F\"\n    },\n    {\n      title: \"Cognitive Chat Console\",\n      href: \"/build/talk\",\n      desc: \"Interact with advanced supervisor agents. Configure conversational schemas, test semantic memory, and trigger isolated command cycles.\",\n      category: \"SIMULATION\",\n      color: \"from-emerald-500/20 to-teal-500/10\",\n      accent: \"#00FF9D\"\n    },\n    {\n      title: \"Proposal Studio\",\n      href: \"/build/proposal\",\n      desc: \"Access instant algorithmic scoping decks, Statement of Work (SOW) exports, and structured delivery schedules in seconds.\",\n      category: \"COMMERCIALS\",\n      color: \"from-indigo-500/20 to-blue-500/10\",\n      accent: \"#3B82F6\"\n    },\n    {\n      title: \"Zero-Trust Sandbox\",\n      href: \"/build/sandbox\",\n      desc: \"Launch air-gapped simulated test traces. Monitor memory bounds and security constraints inside a safe local testing environment.\",\n      category: \"ENCLAVE\",\n      color: \"from-violet-500/20 to-indigo-500/10\",\n      accent: \"#8B5CF6\"\n    },\n    {\n      title: \"Foundry Studio Simulator\",\n      href: \"/build/foundry-studio\",\n      desc: \"Configure multi-agent DAG execution flows, set human-in-the-loop validation milestones, and orchestrate complex work loops.\",\n      category: \"WORKSPACE\",\n      color: \"from-[#009DFF]/20 to-purple-500/10\",\n      accent: \"#009DFF\"\n    },\n    {\n      title: \"Sovereign Asset Marketplace\",\n      href: \"/build/marketplace\",\n      desc: \"Browse robust pre-compiled cognitive configurations, certified legacy enterprise integrations, and specialized agent personas.\",\n      category: \"ASSETS\",\n      color: \"from-pink-500/20 to-rose-500/10\",\n      accent: \"#EC4899\"\n    }\n  ];\n\n  return (\n    <InnerPageShell>\n      <InnerPageHero\n        category=\"Enterprise Build Suite\"\n        title=\"Deploy GFF AI\"\n        highlightedWord=\"GFF AI\"\n        description=\"Navigate our end-to-end deployment lifecycle. Track your journey from diagnostic readiness assessment to continuous secure operations using our specialized suite of interactive calculators, blueprint tools, and sandbox simulators.\"\n      />\n\n      <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-16 pb-24 space-y-24\">\n        {/* SECTION 1: Narrative Journey Timeline */}\n        <section className=\"p-8 lg:p-12 rounded-[32px] border border-white/5 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#080b11] to-[#040507] relative overflow-hidden\">\n          <div className=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-[40%] h-[40%] bg-radial-gradient from-[#009DFF]/5 to-transparent blur-3xl pointer-events-none\" />\n          \n          <div className=\"relative z-10 max-w-[1400px] mx-auto\">\n            <div className=\"flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:items-end justify-between gap-6 mb-12\">\n              <div>\n                <span className=\"text-xs font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest block mb-2\">OPERATIONAL PROTOCOL</span>\n                <h2 className=\"text-2xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight\">The 9-Stage Sovereign Deployment Journey</h2>\n                <p className=\"text-white/60 text-sm mt-2 max-w-[650px] font-light leading-relaxed\">\n                  GFF AI operates on a structured, zero-risk integration lifecycle. Click each phase to observe the timelines, rigorous security standards, and operational artifacts produced at each stage.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n              <div className=\"hidden lg:flex items-center gap-3 text-xs font-mono text-white/40\">\n                <span>STAGE STATUS:</span>\n                <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] font-semibold bg-[#009DFF]/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-[#009DFF]/20\">\n                  {activeStage.label.toUpperCase()} PROTOCOL ACTIVE\n                </span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Interactive Timeline Swapper */}\n            <div className=\"relative overflow-x-auto pb-4 scrollbar-thin scrollbar-thumb-white/10 select-none\">\n              <div className=\"min-w-[900px] flex items-center justify-between relative px-4\">\n                {/* Connecting Line Background */}\n                <div className=\"absolute top-[21px] left-8 right-8 h-[2px] bg-white/5 z-0\" />\n                {/* Active Progress Line */}\n                <div \n                  className=\"absolute top-[21px] left-8 h-[2px] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#E4000F] to-[#009DFF] z-0 transition-all duration-500 ease-out\"\n                  style={{ width: `${((activeStage.num - 1) / 8) * 100}%` }}\n                />\n\n                {JOURNEY_STAGES.map((stage) => {\n                  const isActive = activeStage.id === stage.id;\n                  const isCompleted = stage.num < activeStage.num;\n                  return (\n                    <button\n                      key={stage.id}\n                      onClick={() => setActiveStage(stage)}\n                      className=\"flex flex-col items-center relative z-10 group focus:outline-none\"\n                      style={{ width: \"80px\" }}\n                    >\n                      {/* Step Bubble */}\n                      <div className={`w-11 h-11 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-semibold tracking-tight transition-all duration-300 ${\n                        isActive \n                          ? \"bg-[#04060b] border-[#009DFF] text-[#009DFF] shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,157,255,0.4)] scale-110\" \n                          : isCompleted\n                            ? \"bg-gradient-to-br from-[#E4000F] to-[#009DFF] border-transparent text-white\"\n                            : \"bg-[#020202] border-white/10 text-white/40 group-hover:border-white/30 group-hover:text-white/80\"\n                      }`}>\n                        {stage.num}\n                      </div>\n                      \n                      {/* Label */}\n                      <span className={`text-[11px] mt-3 font-semibold tracking-tight text-center truncate w-full transition-colors duration-300 ${\n                        isActive ? \"text-[#009DFF] font-bold\" : \"text-white/60 group-hover:text-white\"\n                      }`}>\n                        {stage.label}\n                      </span>\n                    </button>\n                  );\n                })}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Interactive Stage Panel Detail */}\n            <div className=\"mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 pt-8 border-t border-white/5 relative z-10\">\n              {/* Left Column: Core Info */}\n              <div className=\"lg:col-span-7 space-y-6\">\n                <div className=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4\">\n                  <span className=\"text-[11px] font-mono font-bold tracking-widest text-[#E4000F] uppercase bg-[#E4000F]/10 border border-[#E4000F]/20 px-3 py-1 rounded\">\n                    PHASE 0{activeStage.num}\n                  </span>\n                  <span className=\"text-[11px] font-mono text-white/40\">|</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-xs text-white/60 font-semibold uppercase font-mono\">TIMELINE: {activeStage.duration}</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-[11px] font-mono text-white/40\">|</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-xs text-[#00FF9D] font-bold uppercase font-mono\">{activeStage.metric}</span>\n                </div>\n\n                <h3 className=\"text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight\">{activeStage.label} Strategy</h3>\n                <p className=\"text-white/70 text-sm leading-relaxed font-light\">{activeStage.description}</p>\n                \n                {activeStage.toolHref && (\n                  <div className=\"pt-2\">\n                    <Link \n                      href={activeStage.toolHref} \n                      className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg text-xs font-semibold text-white bg-white/5 border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/10 transition-all hover:border-[#009DFF]/30 group\"\n                    >\n                      <span>{activeStage.toolLabel}</span>\n                      <svg className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform text-[#009DFF]\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n                        <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={2.5} d=\"M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3\" />\n                      </svg>\n                    </Link>\n                  </div>\n                )}\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Right Column: Key Deliverables & Process Artifacts */}\n              <div className=\"lg:col-span-5 p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 flex flex-col justify-between\">\n                <div>\n                  <h4 className=\"text-xs font-mono font-bold tracking-wider text-white/50 uppercase mb-4\">SYSTEM DELIVERABLES</h4>\n                  <ul className=\"space-y-3\">\n                    {activeStage.artifacts.map((art, idx) => (\n                      <li key={idx} className=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-xs text-white/80\">\n                        <svg className=\"w-4 h-4 text-[#00FF9D] mt-0.5 shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n                          <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={2.5} d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\" />\n                        </svg>\n                        <span className=\"font-medium\">{art}</span>\n                      </li>\n                    ))}\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n\n                <div className=\"mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-white/5 flex items-center justify-between text-[10px] font-mono text-white/30\">\n                  <span>ENCLAVE PRIVACY STATUS</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-[#00FF9D]\">ENFORCED</span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n        {/* SECTION 2: Premium Self-Service Tools Bento Grid */}\n        <section className=\"space-y-8\">\n          <div className=\"text-center max-w-[700px] mx-auto\">\n            <span className=\"text-xs font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest block mb-2\">SELF-SERVICE TERMINAL</span>\n            <h2 className=\"text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight\">Interactive Utility Suites</h2>\n            <p className=\"text-white/60 text-sm mt-3 font-light leading-relaxed\">\n              Verify assumptions, configure topologies, calculate structural ROI multipliers, and test-drive sovereign models. Access direct tools designed for engineering and corporate decision-makers.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-6\">\n            {tools.map((tool) => (\n              <div \n                key={tool.title} \n                className=\"relative overflow-hidden p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#040507]/80 backdrop-blur-xl flex flex-col justify-between hover:border-white/10 transition-all duration-300 group shadow-lg\"\n              >\n                {/* Corner radial glow */}\n                <div className=\"absolute -top-12 -right-12 w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/5 to-transparent rounded-full blur-xl pointer-events-none group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform\" />\n                \n                <div>\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n                    <span \n                      className=\"text-[10px] font-mono font-bold tracking-widest px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded\"\n                      style={{ color: tool.accent, backgroundColor: `${tool.accent}12`, border: `1px solid ${tool.accent}20` }}\n                    >\n                      {tool.category}\n                    </span>\n                    <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/30 font-mono\">STABLE-2026</span>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <h3 className=\"text-[17px] font-bold text-white tracking-tight mt-4 group-hover:text-[#009DFF] transition-colors\">\n                    {tool.title}\n                  </h3>\n                  \n                  <p className=\"mt-3 text-[12.5px] leading-[1.65] text-white/60 font-light\">\n                    {tool.desc}\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n\n                <div className=\"mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-white/5 flex items-center justify-between\">\n                  <Link href={tool.href} className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-white hover:text-[#009DFF] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform\">\n                    <span>LAUNCH UTILITY</span>\n                    <svg className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-white/50 group-hover:text-[#009DFF]\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n                      <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={2.5} d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\" />\n                    </svg>\n                  </Link>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            ))}\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n        {/* SECTION 3: Premium CTA Section */}\n        <PremiumCTA \n          title=\"Ready to Transition From Simulation to Sovereign Production?\"\n          description=\"Initiate your secure deployment workspace inside the GFF AI cloud or set up single-tenant private infrastructure schemas. Speak directly to our senior platform architects.\"\n          primaryLabel=\"Connect with GFF Architects\"\n          primaryHref=\"/#contact\"\n          secondaryLabel=\"Read Security Guide\"\n          secondaryHref=\"/platforms\"\n        />\n      </div>\n    </InnerPageShell>\n  );\n}\n"}}}
